cks asi enne, kui alustame."],"Next":["J\u00e4rgmine"],"You can personalize this later.":["Saad seda hiljem kohandada."],"Loading...":["Laadimine..."],"Press to select":["Vajuta valimiseks"],"Just a moment, this is taking longer than expected.":["\u00dcks hetk, see v\u00f5tab oodatust kauem aega."],"Design":["Kujundus"],"Creating pages with custom content":["Kohandatud sisuga lehtede loomine"],"Setting up site layout":["Veebilehe paigutuse seadistamine"],"Professional":["Professionaalne"],"Friendly":["S\u00f5bralik"],"Inspirational":["Inspiratsiooniallikas"],"Informative":["Informatiivne"],"Persuasive":["Veenev"],"Skip":["J\u00e4ta vahele"],"Added by Launch":["Lisas Launch"],"Start over?":["Alusta otsast?"],"Exit":["V\u00e4lju"],"Processing":["T\u00f6\u00f6tlemine"],"Header Navigation":["P\u00e4ise navigeerimine"],"E.g., We are a yoga studio in London with professionally trained instructors with focus on hot yoga for therapeutic purposes.":["N\u00e4iteks, me oleme Londonis asuv joogastuudio, kus on professionaalselt v\u00e4lja\u00f5ppinud juhendajad, kes keskenduvad terapeutilistel eesm\u00e4rkidel kuumjoogale."],"Single-Page Website":["\u00dchelehek\u00fcljeline veebisait"],"All content displayed on one scrolling page.":["Kogu sisu kuvatakse \u00fchel keritaval lehel."],"Multi-Page Website":["Mitmelehek\u00fcljeline veebisait"],"Multiple interconnected pages.":["Mitmed omavahel seotud lehed."],"Pick Your Site Structure":["Vali oma veebilehe struktuur"],"Share your vision, and we'll craft a website that's perfectly tailored to your needs, ready to launch in no time. Let's begin by learning more about what you're building.":["Jaga oma visiooni ja me loome veebisaidi, mis on t\u00e4iuslikult kohandatud sinu vajadustele ning valmis kiiresti k\u00e4ivitamiseks. Alustame sellest, et saame rohkem teada, mida sa ehitad."],"Launch - AI-Powered Web Creation":["K\u00e4ivitus - tehisintellekti abil veebiloome"],"Customizing Your Experience":["Teie kogemuse kohandamine"],"Designing Your Options":["Valikute kujundamine"],"Please wait while we analyze your inputs and tailor your experience.":["Palun oota, kuni anal\u00fc\u00fcsime sinu sisendeid ja kohandame sinu kogemust."],"Please wait while we build some website options for you to select from.":["Palun oota, kuni loome valikuv\u00f5imalusi sinu veebilehe jaoks."],"Creating blog sample data":["Ajaveebi n\u00e4idisandmete loomine"],"More":["Rohkem"],"Blog Post %s":["Blogipostitus %s"],"Importing shop sample data":["Poen\u00e4idiste andmete importimine"],"%s pages\/posts created in the prior onboarding session will be deleted.":["Eelmise sisseelamisprotsessi k\u00e4igus loodud %s lehte\/postitust kustutatakse."],"Select your site's tone":["Vali oma saidi toon"],"Website title (required)":["Veebisaidi pealkiri (kohustuslik)"],"Hello World Featured Image":["Tere, Maailm tunnuspilt"],"Business":["\u00c4ri"],"eCommerce":["E-kaubandus"],"Landing Page":["Maandumisleht"],"Other":["Muu"],"Landing Page title (required)":["Sihtlehe pealkiri (kohustuslik)"],"E.g., We are an online store specializing in eco-friendly home goods, offering sustainably sourced products to help you live a greener lifestyle.":["Nt. Oleme veebipood, mis on spetsialiseerunud keskkonnas\u00f5bralikele kodutoodetele, pakkudes j\u00e4tkusuutlikult hangitud tooteid, et aidata teil elada rohelisemat eluviisi."],"E.g., A personal finance blog sharing expert tips on budgeting, investing, and achieving financial freedom for young professionals.":["Nt. isikliku rahanduse ajaveeb, mis jagab ekspertide n\u00f5uandeid eelarvestamise, investeerimise ja rahalise vabaduse saavutamise kohta noortele spetsialistidele."],"E.g., A free ebook packed with actionable productivity tips and strategies to help you stay focused, manage your time effectively, and achieve your goals.":["Nt. tasuta e-raamat, mis on t\u00e4is praktilisi tootlikkuse n\u00f5uandeid ja strateegiaid, mis aitavad sul keskenduda, aega t\u00f5husalt hallata ja eesm\u00e4rke saavutada"],"E.g., A personal photography portfolio featuring a collection of landscape, portrait, and street photography, capturing moments from around the world.":["Nt. Isiklik fotograafia portfoolio, mis sisaldab maastiku-, portree- ja t\u00e4navafotograafiat, j\u00e4\u00e4dvustades hetki \u00fcle kogu maailma."],"Describe your business":["Kirjelda oma ettev\u00f5tet"],"Describe your eCommerce website":["Kirjelda oma e-kaubanduse veebilehte"],"Describe your blog":["Kirjelda oma ajaveebi"],"Describe your Landing Page":["Kirjelda oma maandumislehte"],"Describe your website":["Kirjelda oma veebilehte"],"Call-To-Action Link":["\u00dcleskutse link"],"This link will be used in all Call-to-Action buttons, directing visitors to your chosen destination.":["Seda linki kasutatakse k\u00f5igis \u00fcleskutse-nuppudes, suunates k\u00fclastajad valitud sihtkohta."],"What type of website are you creating?":["Millist t\u00fc\u00fcpi veebilehte sa lood?"],"Tell Us About Your Landing Page":["R\u00e4\u00e4gi meile oma sihtlehe kohta"],"Tell Us About Your Website":["R\u00e4\u00e4gi meile oma veebisaidist"],"Share your vision, and we'll craft a landing page that's perfectly tailored to your needs, ready to launch in no time. Let's begin by learning more about what you're building.":["Jaga oma visiooni ja me loome sihitud maandumislehe, mis vastab t\u00e4pselt sinu vajadustele ja on valmis kiiresti k\u00e4ivitamiseks. Alustame, uurides, mida sa ehitad."],"Installing supporting plugins":["Toetavate pluginate paigaldamine"],"Show more questions":["N\u00e4ita rohkem k\u00fcsimusi"],"Let's review your AI-powered recommendations":["Vaatame \u00fcle sinu tehisintellekti soovitused"],"Using the details you provided, our AI suggested the best settings for your site. Take a quick look and confirm everything looks right before moving on.":["Sinu sisendi p\u00f5hjal soovitas meie tehisintellekt veebilehele parimaid s\u00e4tteid. Vaata need \u00fcle ja kinnita, et k\u00f5ik on korras, enne kui edasi l